node.text: After years of planning and engineering, we’re SO excited to share how our Special Edition @airstream_inc Travel Trailer came to life! A 28-foot home on wheels that redefines what it means to travel in comfort and style, this trailer sets a new standard for a well-traveled life 🙌 Head to the link in our bio to learn more!

Shelf styling 101 ✍️ Establishing a palette makes shelves feel pulled together. We love the white, black and neutral tones @melissa_shapiro_interiors chose. Then, cluster a few objects to show off their individuality: frames in different sizes, cannisters in different heights, a chunky vase, a natural element. Play with horizontal and vertical lines, depth and dimension. Keep it simple and don’t forget to make it personal! 

📹: @melissa_shapiro_interiors
🎶: Savage Love, Jason Derulo
